This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a novel approach to learning temporal relationships in time series data using capsule networks. Additionally, the paper also discusses the instantiation parameters learnt by the capsule networks, which is a key aspect of machine learning. 

The paper could also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as capsule networks are a type of neural network architecture. 

Furthermore, the paper discusses the use of capsule networks for vision-related tasks, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision). 

The paper also mentions the use of capsule networks for signal processing, which could place it in the sub-categories of cs.SI (Signal Processing) or cs.SD (Sound).
